# AI Operations Dashboard

AI-powered dashboard integrating POS, booking, and accounting data for real-time business performance monitoring.

## Features
- Tracks revenue, covers, spend per head, labour %
- Trend analysis and exception alerts
- Easy-to-use interface for managers

## Tech Stack
Python | Streamlit | REST APIs | Airtable/PostgreSQL

## Use Case
Managers get actionable insights daily to optimize operations and labour costs.
